<h1>Congratulations on landing work!</h1>

<p>How far in advance are you booked? I ask because canceling means you lose out on over $_yearly_price_difference_ . See, the current pricing for Workshop is _current_price_ and it’s about to go up again.</p>

<p>By canceling now it means you’ll be letting your locked-in introductory rate expire.</p>

<p>The subscription you have now comes out to $<%= current_user.subscription.plan.price %>/<%= current_user.subscription.plan.interval %> and I don’t offer it anymore. Soon I’ll also be limiting the amount of members we let join, so I'd hate to see you not be able to get back in, especially if you fall into a dry spell after you finish work just landed.</p>
 
