<p>Staying signed up now during this time will also let you negotiate from a position of power instead of being necessity.</p>

<p>In fact, even if cancel Workshop, I’d still recommend you find at least one lead to contact everyday.</p>

<p>Looking forward to having you as a customer!</p>

<p>Regards,<br>
	Robert<br>
